description.p:
In even still another aspect of the present invention, a method for making a fibrous structure, the method comprising the steps of:



    

a. providing a PVOH polymer melt composition comprising a hydroxyl polymer comprising at least a PVOH hydroxyl polymer;

b. polymer processing the PVOH polymer melt composition to form a polymeric structure in fiber form; and

c. incorporating the polymeric structure in fiber form into a fibrous structure;

wherein the fibrous structure exhibits a stretch at peak load of at least about 5% and/or at least about 8% and/or at least about 10% and/or a stretch at failure load of at least about 10% and/or at least about 13% and/or at least about 20%, is provided.
